reviewText: ordered this for my daughter and she couldn't wait to get it. She absolutely LOVES teen mom.
Favorite show! So happy I have it on DVD!
I love watching these girls and the girls from teen mom. I know they get a lot of negative feed back, but I think the send a good message to teenage girls.

I ordered this product and was looking forward to it. But when I got it in the mail I opened it and it was Teen Mom season 2 not Teen Mom 2 season 2. I was mad at first but I didn't have this season either but at the same time it didn't fix the problem. But the seller is lucky I wasn't going to demand a refund. But I won't buy from this seller again because online you have to trust that what people try to sell online will be what they post. If you sell things online double check to make sure it's exactly what it says it is.
Not worth the money i was so excited to receive these.  But when i tried to play each episode they were all not playing.. Very disapointing. I would think twice before ordering from amazon again .
